alkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"맞아맞아. 댄스부에선 자주 땀을 흘리니까 항상 가지고 다녀~\n……앗! 이건 깨끗한 거니까 안심해!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event10-06-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"난 유키나랑 바닥을 닦을 테니까,\n사요랑 린코는 장비에 묻은 걸 부탁할게!\n다 닦으면 기타 실드랑 마이크 케이블을 둥글게 말아줘.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event10-06-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"사요・린코","body":"아, 알았어요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event10-06-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"아코는…… 자, 내 손수건을 써.\n스커트 자락에 묻었지?\n팍팍 두드려서 물기를 흡수시켜야 해.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event10-06-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySoun